# What can I do when import fails?

Run a manual import to refresh data in the service:

1.  Go to the **Import** menu and click the [**Start Import**]( https://github.com/alinbogdan/ContDocumentation/blob/master/translations/en/online-help/startup-wizard-concept.md) button.
2.  Wait for the import process to finish.
3.  Check the message again.

If it still indicates that the import has failed, please [contact support](https://github.com/alinbogdan/ContDocumentation/blob/master/translations/en/online-help/report-problem-or-wish-for-improvement.md).
